  <name>Zippy</name>
  <summary>Professional Folder Compression Tool</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Zippy is a powerful GUI application for compressing large folders efficiently. 
      It features smart exclusions to skip unnecessary files like node_modules, .git, 
      and build artifacts, reducing archive size significantly.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Smart exclusions for development files</li>
      <li>Progress tracking and cancellation</li>
      <li>Modern PyQt6 interface</li>
      <li>Support for large folder compression</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
